</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uleifelf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Leifelf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Holy Defender</span><br>  Posts: 1004<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/22/02 9:57:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15644.topic&index=25>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: It doesnt matter</span><hr size=1> Although I don't often do it, I will have to agree with Beld.  The  75% war, 25% clr description is getting off the mark.  We are 100% Paladin.  <br>
