59 Knight <BR>
Bristlebane Server <BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bpaladinsofnorrath.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=siegfried>Siegfried</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Wandering Knight</span><br>  Posts: 183<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/23/02 11:47:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15644.topic&index=26>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: It doesnt matter</span><hr size=1> A fully AA'd Paladin with top-end gear is an EQ force to be reckoned with.<br>
